julev+N+Sem/Dummytag+Cmp/SgNom:julev R ;
laadth+N+Sem/Dummytag+Cmp/SgNom:laadth R ;
maadth+N+Sem/Dummytag+Cmp/SgNom+Dial/-NOR:maadth R ; ! maadtege
orr+N+Sem/Dummytag+Cmp/SgNom:orr R ;
!roest+N+Sem/Dummytag:roest R ;
