!! # All nouns with possessives

LEXICON Noun !!â # **@CODE@**
!! Splitting nouns in NounNoPx, NounPx (with a P.Px.add
!! flag) and NounPxKin (with a P.Nom3Px.add flag)
                          NounNoPx  ; !!â * **@CODE@** = words in this noun lexicon do not get any possessive inflectionb
                @P.Px.add@ NounPx    ; !!â * **@CODE@** = these nouns do get possessive inflection, except for 3. person nominative, which is usually only used with kinship terms (see next)
                @P.Px.add@ NounPxKin ; !!â * **@CODE@** = these nouns get full possessive inflection, including 3. person nominative - except that the 3. person nominative has been removed in the South SĂĄmi description. The reason for that change needs to be documented here.
! @P.Px.add@@P.Nom3Px.add@ NounPxKin ;

LEXICON NounPxKin ! Dette er lemma som kan fĂĽ flere possesive suffikser enn andre lemma.
